creatures:
- name: Lich
  statblock:
    custom_statblock: |
      **Armor Class** 17 (natural armor)  
      **Hit Points** 135 (rollable(dice=18d8 + 54,dicelabel=Hit Points))  
      **Speed** 30 ft.  

      ---

      |str|dex|con|int|wis|cha|
      |:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|
      |number(name=str,label=Strength,value=11)|number(name=dex,label=Dexterity,value=16)|number(name=con,label=Constitution,value=16)|number(name=int,label=Intelligence,value=20)|number(name=wis,label=Wisdom,value=14)|number(name=cha,label=Charisma,value=16)|
      |(mod5e(show_symbol,value=str,dice=1d20+n,dicelabel=Strength Check))|(mod5e(show_symbol,value=dex,dice=1d20+n,dicelabel=Dexterity Check))|(mod5e(show_symbol,value=con,dice=1d20+n,dicelabel=Constitution Check))|(mod5e(show_symbol,value=int,dice=1d20+n,dicelabel=Intelligence Check))|(mod5e(show_symbol,value=wis,dice=1d20+n,dicelabel=Wisdom Check))|(mod5e(show_symbol,value=cha,dice=1d20+n,dicelabel=Charisma Check))|

      ---

      **Saving Throws** Con rollable(dice=1d20+10,label=+10,dicelabel=Constitution Saving Throw), Int rollable(dice=1d20+12,label=+12,dicelabel=Intelligence Saving Throw), Wis rollable(dice=1d20+9,label=+9,dicelabel=Wisdom Saving Throw)  
      **Skills** Arcana rollable(dice=1d20+19,label=+19,dicelabel=Arcana Check), History rollable(dice=1d20+12,label=+12,dicelabel=History Check), Insight rollable(dice=1d20+9,label=+9,dicelabel=Insight Check), Perception rollable(dice=1d20+9,label=+9,dicelabel=Perception Check)  
      **Damage Resistances** cold, lightning, necrotic  
      **Damage Immunities** poison; bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing from nonmagical attacks  
      **Condition Immunities** charmed, exhaustion, frightened, paralyzed, poisoned  
      **Senses** truesight 120 ft., Passive Perception 19  
      **Languages** Common plus up to five other languages  
      **Challenge** 21 (33,000 XP) or 22 (41,000 XP) when encountered in lair  
      **Proficiency Bonus** +7  

      ---

      ***Legendary Resistance (3/Day).*** If the lich fails a saving throw, it can choose to succeed instead.

      ***Rejuvenation.*** If it has a phylactery, a destroyed lich gains a new body in rollable(dice=1d10,dicelabel=Rejuvenation) days, regaining all its hit points and becoming active again. The new body appears within 5 feet of the phylactery.

      ***Turn Resistance.*** The lich has advantage on saving throws against any effect that turns undead.

      ***Spellcasting.*** The lich is an 18th-level spellcaster. Its spellcasting ability is Intelligence (spell save DC 20, rollable(dice=1d20+12,label=+12,dicelabel=To Hit [Spell Attack]) to hit with spell attacks). The lich has the following wizard spells prepared:

      Cantrips (at will) [mage hand](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/mage-hand), [prestidigitation](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/prestidigitation), [ray of frost](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/ray-of-frost)    
      1st level (4 slots) [detect magic](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/detect-magic), [magic missile](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/magic-missile), [shield](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/shield), [thunderwave](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/thunderwave)    
      2nd level (3 slots) [detect thoughts](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/detect-thoughts), [invisibility](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/invisibility), [Melf's acid arrow](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/Melf's-acid-arrow), [mirror image](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/mirror-image)    
      3rd level (3 slots) [animate dead](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/animate-dead), [counterspell](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/counterspell), [dispel magic](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/dispel-magic), [fireball](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/fireball)    
      5th level (3 slots) [blight](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/blight), [dimension door](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/dimension-door)    
      5th level (3 slots) [cloudkill](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/cloudkill), [scrying](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/scrying)    
      6th level (1 slot) [disintegrate](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/disintegrate), [globe of invulnerability](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/globe-of-invulnerability)    
      7th level (1 slot) [finger of death](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/finger-of-death), [plane shift](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/plane-shift)    
      8th level (1 slot) [dominate monster](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/dominate-monster), [power word stun](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/power-word-stun)    
      9th level (1 slot) [power word kill](https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/power-word-kill)    

      ## Actions

      ***Paralyzing Touch.*** *Melee Spell Attack* rollable(dice=1d20+12,label=+12,dicelabel=To Hit [Paralyzing Touch]) to hit, reach 5 ft., one creature. *Hit:* rollable(dice=3d6,dicelabel=Damage [Paralyzing Touch]) cold damage. The target must succeed on a DC 18 Constitution saving throw or be ***paralyzed*** for 1 minute. The target can repeat the saving throw at the end of each of its turns, ending the effect on itself on a success.

      ## Legendary Actions

      ***Cantrip.*** The lich casts a cantrip.

      ***Paralyzing Touch (Costs 2 Actions).*** The lich uses its Paralyzing Touch.

      ***Frightening Gaze (Costs 2 Actions).*** The lich fixes its gaze on one creature it can see within 10 feet of it. The target must succeed on a DC 18 Wisdom saving throw against this magic or become ***frightened*** for 1 minute. The ***frightened*** target can repeat the saving throw at the end of each of its turns, ending the effect on itself on a success. If a target's saving throw is successful or the effect ends for it, the target is immune to the lich's gaze for the next 24 hours.

      ***Disrupt Life (Costs 3 Actions).*** Each non-undead creature within 20 feet of the lich must make a DC 18 Constitution saving throw against this magic, taking rollable(dice=6d6,dicelabel=Damage [Disrupt Life]) necrotic damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.

